@w05

; 宿屋・朝のロビー
@bg f=0002
@mu f=guild
[texton w=1]
Next morning.[k]
[マックス f=03]「Well, I'm off to see Maria for the first time in a while!」[k]
[テオ f=02]「Say hi to Maria for me, [マックス].」[k]
It seems that everyone went to visit family or find entertainment.[k]
Well, I have to go to the guild...[k]
[textoff]
@fg c=ミューズ e=通常 f=05
