; 宿屋の一室
@saveon
@fg c=ミューズ e=通常 f=06 b
@bg f=0001
@mu f=guild
[texton w=1]
[テオ e=通常 f=05]「Hey, [ミューズ]. About the other day...」[k]
[ミューズ f=06]「...」[k]
[テオ f=05]「You said you can't go back to your village, why is that?」[k]
@fg c=ミューズ f=10
[ミューズ f=10]「...」[k]
[ミューズ] awkwardly looks away from me and doesn't speak.[k]
I guess she doesn't want to tell me.[k]
[テオ f=12]「Sorry! I didn't mean to intrude if you don't want to tell me...」[k]
[ミューズ v=vg200 f=10]「...I can't get into the village.」[k]
[テオ f=05]「Eh?」[k]
[ミューズ v=vg201 f=10]「I really want to go back to my village. My family and the people in the village may be waiting. But once I enter the village, it's the end for me...」[k]
[テオ f=05]「Once you enter the village, it's the end? What do you mean?」[k]
[ミューズ f=10]「...」[k]
[ミューズ v=vg202 f=10]「...I'll tell you. What happened, and why I can't go back...」[k]
[textoff]
@fa
@out

; ミューズの回想・過去の話
@mu f=anxiety
[texton w=1]
As you can tell from me, gnomes, are small and frail.[k]
We could never win a war with another race. So in order to protect ourselves, we built settlements in remote caves and lived inconspicuously.[k]
I was also born in a village like that. There, we lived a modest life, growing crops that grew in the dark and selling ore.[k]
[textoff]
@out
@bg f=0065
[texton w=1]
One day, a group of human bandits came to our village from somewhere.[k]
They probably noticed that the ore from our village fetches a high price.[k]
They were armed and said that from that day, they would rule the village.[k]
Of course that's a ridiculous demand.[k]
...But none of the adults in the village defied the bandits.[k]
Because when you resist... you can't win.[k]
[textoff]
@out
[texton w=1]
So the bandits' rule began.[k]
Adults, children, and the elderly were all sent out to mine for ore, and were forced to work day and night.[k]
Most of the profits from the ore trade went to the bandits, and we gnomes were given only a little food and forced to work.[k]
The village and our freedom wasn't ours any more.[k]
[textoff]
@out
@bg f=event102 p0=02
[texton w=1]
The young women of the village were gathered in one of the large houses in the settlement.[k]
They were forced to live as the mountain bandits' playthings.[k]
They were forced to wear only the bare minimum of clothing and humiliated day after day at the whim of the bandits.[k]
[if exp='f.killedBanditsRapeGnome']
	; 回避ルート・回避可能なのは最初の１人だけ
	Fortunately, I wasn't targeted by them and was able to preserve my chastity.[k]
	However, some girls couldn't endure a life of sexual servitude and took their own lives.[k]
	@eval exp='f.killedBanditsRapeGnome = false'
[else]
	; 寝取られルート
	[textoff]
	[texton w=2]
	@bg f=event99 p1=02
	...That's when I first experienced a man.[k]
	Some girls couldn't endure a life of sexual servitude and took their own lives.[k]
	@eval exp='o.ミューズ.sexCount.other += 12'
	@eval exp='o.ミューズ.firstPartnerKey = "other"'
	@eval exp='o.ミューズ.loversCount += 5'
	@eval exp='o.ミューズ.pourCount += 6'
[endif]
[textoff]
@out

@bg f=0066
[texton w=1]
One day...[k]
I and a few other girls happened to be unobserved by the bandits.[k]
We were near the exit of the cave at the time, so we decided to take this opportunity to escape from the village.[k]
But on our way out, we were discovered. They chased us angrily toward the exit of the cave.[k]
...Then, the other girls shielded me, so I could escape.[k]
"You at least, should be free". That's what they said to me.[k]
[textoff]
@out

@bg f=0054
@mu f=calm
[texton w=1]
Thanks to them, I was able to escape from the bandits.[k]
...But my heart was filled with anxiety.[k]
I had never left the village, and I had never lived alone. I sometimes wished I could have stayed with my family and everyone else, even if life was hard.[k]
But I did not return to the village.[k]
I didn't want to waste the sacrifice of the girls who helped me leave...[k]
[textoff]
@out

@bg f=0019
[texton w=1]
I set out for the town. And I managed to reach Sapphire City.[k]
But I didn't know what to do. Although I was free, I had no one to rely on, and I was at a loss as to how I should live from now on.[k]
While I was wandering around the streets lost, some people from the guild took me in.[k]
There I learned that there was a way of life called "adventuring". I learned that I could earn money as an adventurer by making use of gnomes' magical powers.[k]
Of course, the guild members also told me that there are other ways to work.[k]
But... I chose to be an adventurer.[k]
Because I wanted to become stronger. [r]
Realizing that if I was weak, I would be unfairly dominated, I didn't want to live that way anymore.[k]
...But in reality, it wasn't so easy.[k]
I was a low-level, inexperienced adventurer, and it was difficult to find a party willing to hire me.[k]
Eventually, the guild members began urging me to look for other work, and I almost gave up on being an adventurer.[k]
One day...[k]
[textoff]
@out

; 回想・ゲーム序盤のテオとの出会いの場面
@fg c=5001 b
@bg f=0047
[texton w=1]
[name n=&'o.テオ.displayName' f=theo_sepia_01]「Oh... are you the gnome who's joining my party?」[k]
[name n=&'o.ミューズ.displayName' f=gno1_sepia_05]「...!」[k]
[name n=&'o.ミューズ.displayName' f=gno1_sepia_06]「... ∗nod∗」[k]
@fgf c=5002
[name n=&'o.テオ.displayName' f=theo_sepia_02]「Ah, good. I'm [テオ]. Nice to meet you. And you are?」[k]
[name n=&'o.ミューズ.displayName' v=vg001 f=gno1_sepia_05]「...[ミューズ].」[k]
@fgf c=5001
[name n=&'o.テオ.displayName' f=theo_sepia_01]「I'm looking forward to working with you, [ミューズ].」[k]
[name n=&'o.ミューズ.displayName' f=gno1_sepia_06]「... ∗nod∗」[k]
One party leader hired me.[k]
A person kindly reached out to me and said we would work together. It was... you.[k]
[textoff]
@out

@fg c=ミューズ e=通常 f=24 b
@bg f=0001
[texton w=1]
[テオ f=06]「...」[k]
[ミューズ v=vg203 f=24]「If you hadn't called on me, I would have been helpless for a long time... Thanks to you, I found my place in the world...」[k]
@fg c=ミューズ e=通常・大 f=48
[ミューズ] then approached me and held the hem of my clothes tightly.[k]
[テオ f=05]「[ミューズ]...」[k]
[ミューズ v=vg204 f=48]「I want you to keep me close to you... If you abandon me, I...」[k]
[ミューズ]'s voice is getting shakier and shakier as she struggles to speak.[k]
[テオ f=02]「It's okay, [ミューズ]. I'm not going to abandon you.」[k]
[ミューズ v=vg205 f=47]「Captain...!」[k]
@cl
[ミューズ]'s eyes were moistening and she gently leaned her body against my arm.[k]
I hug her shoulder.[k]
She is shy and seemingly unreliable, but she is here because she summoned up her courage and overcame great hardship.[k]
She is so small and fragile in my arms that I can't help but want to protect her.[k]
I would never let [ミューズ] be harmed again.[k]
[テオ f=01]「By the way, what happened to the village where you lived?」[k]
@fg c=ミューズ e=通常・大 f=10
[ミューズ v=vg206 f=10]「I don't know, I haven't been back for a long time. But...」[k]
[ミューズ v=vg207 f=10]「Maybe even now... it's still under the control of those bandits.」[k]
[テオ f=12]「Oh no...!」[k]
What a thing to imagine. How can it be that the weak were so close, but continued to suffer without our knowledge?[k]
[テオ f=06]「...」[k]
...I didn't become an adventurer just for money or fame.[k]
I wanted to do this because I wanted to help people... I wanted to be of service to the world, like my father.[k]
[テオ f=05]「Hey, [ミューズ]. Take me to your village.」[k]
@fg c=ミューズ e=通常・大 f=05
[ミューズ v=vg208 f=05]「What...?」[k]
[テオ f=06]「I can't ignore this. I'm an adventurer.」[k]
@fg c=ミューズ e=通常・大 f=58
[ミューズ v=vg209 f=58]「Don't tell me you're going to fight those people...?!」[k]
[ミューズ v=vg210 f=57]「Don't! There are too many of them... They are underhanded and dangerous.」[k]
[テオ f=05]「I understand. But I can't just look the other way. People who are being oppressed...!」[k]
@fg c=ミューズ e=通常・大 f=30
[ミューズ f=30]「...」[k]
[テオ f=05]「No...?」[k]
[ミューズ v=vg211 f=30]「...I understand. I'll tell you where it is.」[k]
[ミューズ v=vg212 f=30]「But please don't do anything reckless...! If anything happens to you... I...」[k]
[テオ f=02]「I know. Thanks for your concern.」[k]
[textoff]
@out
@w05

[texton]
According to [ミューズ], her home village is in [b]a cave[/b] at the bottom of Landon Canyon.[k]
We should go there as soon as we're ready.[k]
[textoff]
@out
@w05
[hoteloff]


;◇主人公イベント08
*theo_08

; 洞窟内・ノームの村
@saveon
[texton w=0]
[テオ f=05]「This is [ミューズ]'s home village...!」[k]
A small settlement was built a short distance into the cave.[k]
In a pit visible at the far end of the village, emaciated gnomes are being put to work mining.[k]
A few large human men are watching the gnomes with their weapons at the ready. They are probably the bandits.[k]
[name n=Bandit f=bandit_blue_01]「Mm? Who the hell are you?!」[k]
One of the men in the bandit group noticed our presence![k]
[テオ f=05]「We are adventurers here under orders from the Sapphire City Guard. We are here to arrest you bandits occupying this gnome village.」[k]
I had consulted the Sapphire City Guard about this matter beforehand.[k]
The bandits were so cunning that they had the gnome chief write a memorandum delegating the right to govern the village to the bandits.[k]
Of course, the document would have been forced to be written by the bandits through intimidation. However, it had become the official proof of the contract.[k]
In fact, the Sapphire City Guard was aware of the situation in this village. However, because of that contract, they couldn't touch this village until now.[k]
I carefully explained what [ミューズ] had told me to the security team. The security team agreed that it was an unlawful contract and that it was invalid.[k]
Between the bandits, who had a bad reputation, and us, who had built up their trust with our achievements as adventurers, it goes without saying which of us they believed.[k]
The security team gave our party the task of apprehending them. This means we are here with the endorsement of Sapphire City.[k]
[name n=Bandit f=bandit_red_01]「You're arresting us?」[k]
[name n=Bandit f=bandit_blue_01]「Don't let the adventurers get the better of you. Hey! You guys! There's an intruder in our village!」[k]
When the bandit called out, his fellow bandits gathered around him.[k]
[name n="Bandit Leader" f=bandit_yellow_01]「What's going on? Who are these guys?」[k]
[name n=Bandit f=bandit_blue_01]「Some adventurers are trying to pick a fight with us!」[k]
[name n="Bandit Leader" f=bandit_yellow_01]「What the?! Hey, guys! Let's beat these guys to a pulp!」[k]
[テオ f=06]「...!」[k]
The bandits suddenly attacked![k]
[textoff]

